{
  "stem": "9262.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think they were giving us a little blob of margarine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, this is supposed to be food for 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, when you go, the following day, to work, you've got to have something to eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, I knew that if I won't eat this, if I have it the next day, they either will beat me to death, shoot me, or kill me because they will say that I stole it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I didn't want this to happen to me, so I always ate it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I-- as I received it, I was eating it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "People said, oh, you've got to keep something for tomorrow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What will you do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're eating all this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You can die.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You can die there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, well, you die, you die.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said, you can't help that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were given this ration, and we were eating this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some ate it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some didn't.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And after a few weeks, they changed the kommandos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had to go and work in different sections, different places.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one high-ranking SS officer came, and he called out, who wants to volunteer to work in [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] animal clinic?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, he spoke German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "A lot of them didn't understand, but when he said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [GERMAN], which, in German, means animal clinic, I volunteered.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I went to work there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
